&lt;p&gt;
活动主要以讨论为主，主题为校园应用开发，主要涉及学校的各种服务，如BBS客户端、自习空闲教室查询、图书查询续借、课表查询、学校活动通知等内容。具体安排如下：&lt;br&gt;
The event focuses on discussion of the development of campus applications, which provide services for students, for example, BBS client, information inquiries(eg. available study halls, books, school timetable), event notifications etc. The event plan is following.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
主题：Android校园应用开发之XML/JSON数据交换&lt;br&gt;
Theme: The Development of Campus Applications on Android - Data Exchange through XML/JSON
&lt;/p&gt;

流程：&lt;br&gt;
Procedure：&lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;19:00 - 19:30    校园应用开发介绍：&lt;br&gt;
19:00 - 19:30 The Introduction of The Development of Campus Applications:&lt;br&gt;
        针对校园环境，向同学提供服务（查询、通知、交流等）&lt;br&gt;
        According to the campus environment, the app provides services for students (inquiries, notifications, communication etc.)
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;19:40 - 20:10    基于XML的校园BBS客户端应用开发实例：&lt;br&gt;
19:40 - 20:10 The Demo of Campus BBS Client Based On XML：&lt;br&gt;
        讲解Android对XML的解析方式&lt;br&gt;
        Introduction of Parsing XML on Android&lt;br&gt;
        演示BBS客户端&lt;br&gt;
        Demonstration of BBS Client&lt;br&gt;
        BBS客户端开发现状&lt;br&gt;
        The Development Status of BBS Client&lt;br&gt;
        开发过程中存在的问题&lt;br&gt;
        The Problems Found During Developing
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;20:20 - 22:00    讨论：&lt;br&gt;
20:20 - 22:00 Discussion：&lt;br&gt;
        校园应用开发的需求分析&lt;br&gt;
        The Requirement Analysis of Developing Campus App&lt;br&gt;
        nForum API介绍&lt;br&gt;
